This paper focuses on using Graph Neural Networks for learning coordination mechanisms in teams of robots, which is a problem in robotics (cs.RO). The use of neural networks for learning also falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of message passing and updating internal states, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG). The problem of estimating network topology is related to control systems (cs.SY), and the use of distributed algorithms is related to multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
